# Exploration: od

## Rounds
  round 0: 108 isolated cumulative, 133 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 123 isolated cumulative, 31 identical in round (refinement)
  round 2: 143 isolated cumulative, 32 identical in round (refinement)
  round 3: 143 isolated cumulative, 32 identical in round (refinement)

## Observed: 18/21 flags
  12 solo, 6 via combination
  3 additional error-differentiated
  3 behavioral aliases detected

Aliases: -A = --address-radix, -N = --read-bytes, -j = --skip-bytes, -t = --format, -v = --output-duplicates

